TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: Xy dng gii php tng la lp ng dng da trn Modsecurity
Tc gi lun vn: Trn c Mnh Kha: CNTT2020B
Ngi hng dn: PGS.TS. Trn Quang c
T kha (Keyword): Modsecurity; ng dng hc my trong gii php tng la
lp ng dng; H thng pht hin truy vn bt thng.
Ni dung tm tt:
1. L do la chn ti.
Ngy nay, cng vi s pht trin mnh m v bng n ca cng ngh thng
tin ko theo cc nguy c gy mt an ton an ninh thng tin trn khng gian mng
ngy mt gia tng v c s lng v mc nguy him. Xu hng tn cng vo
cc cng thng tin in t dn tr thnh xu hng chnh gy rt nhiu kh khn
cho nhng ngi qun tr bo mt. Vic nhng k tn cng ly cp cc thng tin,
ph hoi hay thay i, xuyn tc ni dung thng tin ti cc cng thng tin in t
mang li nhng thit hi v cng ln c bit l i vi cc cng thng tin quan
trng ca chnh ph.
Cc c quan nh nc, cc t chc chnh ph v ang c nhiu bin php
tch cc trong vic phng chng v pht hin tn cng website, trong , gii php
trin khai tng la lp ng dng web (Web Application Firewall - WAF) l mt
trong nhng gii php ti u nht nhm m bo an ton thng tin cho cc cng
thng tin in t.
Hin ti, trn th trng c rt nhiu sn phm v WAF trong c c
nhng bn thng mi v m ngun m. Cc gii php WAF thng mi thng
c nh gi cao hn tuy nhin vic s dng cc phn mm, thit b thng mi
ny tim n ri ro v vic r r thng tin. Chnh v vy, lm ch cng ngh v
pht trin cc phn mm, thit b l thc s cn thit nhm m bo an ninh an
ton cho cc cng thng tin in t quan trng. Nhn thy c tim nng v li
ch m tng la lp ng dng web mng li, ti quyt nh chn ti Xy
dng gii php tng la lp ng dng da trn Modsecurity nghin cu v
gii php cng ngh ny.
2. Tnh cp thit ca ti.
Cc loi tng la ph bin hin nay a s u s dng cc thng tin tng
mng (network layer) v tng vn chuyn (transport layer) ch yu l s cng (port
number) v giao thc ngn chn cc tn cng, truy cp tri php. Chnh v vic
cc gii php tng la ny vn cho php gi tin i n cc dch v nh my ch
web, dns, FTP nn vic bo v cc dch v ny ngi qun tr c th to ra cc ng
3
dng vi m ngun an ton. Hin ti, c nhiu ti liu hng dn lp trnh an ton,
tuy nhin, khng phi lc no cc nh pht trin ng dng cng nm vng v lm
theo cc hng dn ny dn n vic mc li trong qu trnh thit k, ci t l
iu khng th trnh khi. H thng pht hin/chng tn cng (Intrusion Detection
System-IDS/Intrusion Prevention System-IPS) l mt gii php c a ra bo
v cc ng dng web nh trang thng tin in t.
C hai hng tip cn chnh trong vic pht trin cc IDS/IPS. Gii php
s dng mu nhn dng (signature-based IDS) v gii php da vo hnh vi
(behavior-based IDS). Cc k thut da vo mu nhn dng pht hin tn cng
bng cch so snh ni dung gi tin vi cc du hiu nhn dng (signature) t c s
d liu to sn. Nu c s trng khp th h thng s cnh bo c tn cng (v
d h thng Snort). u im ca hng tip cn ny l chnh xc cao, tuy nhin,
nhc im l n khng th pht hin cc dng tn cng mi trong khi thc trng
s lng m c khng ngng gia tng theo tng thng, nm. i vi k thut da
vo hnh vi (behavior-based IDS), IDS/IPS s xy dng tp d liu (profile) m
t hot ng bnh thng ca h thng m chng bo v. Nu c tnh ca lung
d liu (traffic) khc vi tp m h thng hc trc , h thng IDS/IPS s
thng bo l c tn cng (v d h thng Bro). u im ca phng php tip cn
ny l c th pht hin c cc dng tn cng mi. Tuy nhin nhc im l t l
cnh bo sai cao.
Tuy nhin, vn chnh ca cc h thng IDS/IPS l chng khng hiu
c logic ca giao thc tc l chng khng th bit c mt gi tin HTTP ng
hay sai nh dng. gii quyt vn ny tng la lp ng dng web (Web
Application firewallWAF) c a vo ng dng v s dng nhm pht hin
nhng loi tn cng m IDS/IPS khng th pht hin.
3. Mc ch ca ti
Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn bao gm hai ni dung chnh:
- Tm hiu v cc c trng c bn ca website, la chn phn tch cc c
trng trch chn ra cc c trng tt nht.
- Hiu r kin trc trin khai ca tng la lp ng dng, tm hiu cc thut
ton hc my, vn dng xy dng v pht trin h thng tng la lp ng dng
kt hp hc my da trn tng la ModSecurity m ngun m.
4. Ni dung ca lun vn
Lun vn c chia ra lm 05 chng c th nh sau:

CHNG 4: KT LUN
CHNG 5: TI LIU THAM KHO
5. ng gp v hng pht trin ca lun vn
Vi mc tiu nghin cu gii php xy dng tng la lp ng dng da
trn Modsecurity, lun vn tp trung vo nghin cu cc phng php pht hin
bt thng da trn hc my thng k kt hp vi tng la m ngun m
Modsecuriy xy dng mt tng la ng dng web c th ngn chn, phng
chng mt s dng tn cng. Mt s kt qu chnh t c trong lun vn: (i)
Cung cp mt ci nhn tng quan v tnh hnh tn cng ca tin tc vo cc trang
thng tin in t ng thi a ra cc gii php ng ph vi tnh hnh trn (ii)
tm hiu v lit k mt s nguy c mt an ton thng tin thng qua cc k thut tn
cng web, a ra nhng l hng thng gp v cch thc ngn chn trong thc t.
(iii) vn dng cc c s l thuyt ca cc thut ton hc my tin hnh a vo th
nghim thc t cc truy vn u vo to ra cc ngng gi tr lm c s i
snh vi tng la modsecurity. (iv) Da trn cc c s l thuyt v HTTP, cc
c trng trong header HTTP tin hnh xy dng gii php tng la lp ng dng
5
vi ch reverse proxy tch hp vi tng la m ngun m Modsecuriy phn
tch v a ra kt qu i vi cc truy vn u vo.
Qua kt qu thc nghim cc truy vn trong thc t, mc d lun vn khng
c tnh mi nhng gii php xy dng tng la lp ng dng da trn
Modsecurity c kh nng trin khai trong mt s ng dng thc t, h tr cho cc
doanh nghip, t chc vi nh hng l gii quyt cc dng tn cng v cc trang,
cng thng tin in t - mt trong nhng vn cp thit hin nay.
Hin ti h thng a ra cnh bo truy vn bt thng hay bnh thng c
chnh xc cha c cao v cn hon thin trong tng lai. Mt s hng pht
trin tip theo ca lun vn c th l: (i) Tham kho, thu thp v xy dng thm
cho b d liu hc my phong ph hn t tng kh nng nhn din chnh xc
hn cho h thng bng cch s dng cc logs ca cc trang web; thu thp cc b
d liu kim th trn mng Internet. (ii) Tip tc th nghim trn nhiu cc thut
ton hc my vi cc kch bn khc nhau v b d liu khc nhau a ra c
gi tr ngng t xc nh c kt qu chnh xc hn. (iii) Tin hnh so snh
cc loi tng la ng dng web ph bin trn th trng hin nay v d nh
AQTRONIX WebKnight, Barracuda Web Application Firewall, SecureSphere Web
Application Firewall, Dch v Web Application Firewall ca Cyberoam vi tng
la Modsecurity pht hin c u, nhc im ca h thng. (iv) Hon thin,
cp nht thng xuyn b lut ca h thng c th pht hin ngn chn v cnh
bo cc truy vn bt thng t nhiu hnh thc tn cng khc nhau ca tin tc.
